v1 routes:
    user:
        -user can log in-> return user + token
        -user can log out=> return nothing
        -user can sign up => returns logged in user and token
        -user can change password => returns nothing or maybe a token
    
    thread
        - a user can create a thread => returns thread or maybe thread id?
        - a user can delete a threads original post leaving the rest of the rest of the thread
    
    post:
        - a user can post
        - a user can edit its own post
        - a user can delete own post